  m_text: 'Vending Machine Rules


    1. Inform your supervisor when soda is out
    of stock

    2. Limit 2 uses per person

    3. Interact with the machine to
    receive an ammo crate

    4. Ammo crates cost 100 PTO each

    5. Hold the
    weapon you want to receive for ammo for

    6. Interact with the ammo crate
    to store the ammo'
